Class RoboDialogFragment

All Implemented Interfaces:
android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, android.content.DialogInterface.OnCancelListener, android.content.DialogInterface.OnDismissListener, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener
public abstract class RoboDialogFragment
extends android.app.DialogFragment

Provides an injected DialogFragment based on the native HONEY_COMB+ Fragments. A RoboDialogFragment will see all its members and views injected after onViewCreated(View, Bundle).

Charles Munger
